{"id": "1388070499476705331", "channel_id": "1388070499476705331", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：珊EP·石化藝術，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：珊EP·石化藝術\n她答應過你，一定會帶你一起回家。\n——以恆久的姿態，回到靜謐的、奇蹟和美的家鄉。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST：\"Sanga EP·Art of Corallization \"was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\nMorimens OST：\"Sanga EP·Art of Corallization\"\nShe promised to take you home. Together.\n—In eternal form, to that quiet homeland of miracles and beauty.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-06-27T08:16:36.178000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "behave", "emoji_id": "1361909598067625984", "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1388070499975696455", "filename": "OST-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1746599, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388070499476705331/1388070499975696455/OST-.jpg?ex=69ccd464&is=69cb82e4&hm=c81f2d262000ad1a1ff79b1034f8c19bdf456d6f03167547497f7decd40a7491&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1388070499476705331", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：珊EP·石化藝術", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1388070621589536840", "channel_id": "1388070499476705331", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.靈魂轉移-Soul Transference-**\n\n咦？你好像和剛剛變得不一樣了？\n是眼神更加明亮了？是舉止更加活潑了？還是這具平庸的軀殼內，已經改換了靈魂的主人？\n\n\"Oh? You seem... different now.\"\nHas your gaze grown brighter? Your movements more vivid? Or has this mediocre shell welcomed a new soul?", "timestamp": "2025-06-27T08:17:05.292000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1388070621682073661", "filename": "1.-Soul_Transference-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 3106604, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388070499476705331/1388070621682073661/1.-Soul_Transference-.mp3?ex=69ccd481&is=69cb8301&hm=e8a8e8e91142c98a8de457dbdd4e8fbf6afa0cd32fa69d73e32c3710ab647b4b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1388070499476705331", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：珊EP·石化藝術", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1388070707384291440", "channel_id": "1388070499476705331", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.純白宮殿-The Alabaster Palace-**\n\n白色的珊瑚蔓延出枝椏，生長出純白的宮殿。\n畸形的廊柱中，有多彩的游魚自在穿梭。\n身體在下沉、靈魂在飄蕩。\n你心甘情願地失去呼吸，與她一起沉溺、沉溺，沉溺在白色的幻夢裡。\n那是海的奇蹟，那是溫暖的藍色家鄉。\n\nWhite coral branches twist into towering spires, birthing a palace of bone-pale splendor.\nBetween its malformed columns, prismatic fish weave their endless dance.\nYour body sinks. Your spirit floats.\nYou surrender breath willingly, drowning, drowning... Drowning with her in this pearlescent delirium.\nIt is the ocean's miracle. It is your warm, blue homeland.", "timestamp": "2025-06-27T08:17:25.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1388070707073777756", "filename": "2.-The_Alabaster_Palace-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 5752364, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388070499476705331/1388070707073777756/2.-The_Alabaster_Palace-.mp3?ex=69ccd495&is=69cb8315&hm=777c26c8644148ef83f66e21f9d1101fa2ecb231b93c8ebac3a8676f6446ba40&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1388070499476705331", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：珊EP·石化藝術", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1388070774946005164", "channel_id": "1388070499476705331", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.美的死亡-Death by Beauty-**\n\n生於美，死於美。\n她是天才、瘋子、魔鬼，她是冷漠的劊子手，也是你溫情脈脈的家人。\n她用熾熱的愛，將你炮製成一件完美的作品。\n她把你擁抱，將你冰冷的手牽起。她會帶著你，與她一起回到藝術的家鄉。\n\nBorn of beauty. Perfected in death.\nShe is genius, madwoman, devil. The executioner whose hands cradle your face like family.\nHer scorching love preserves you: a flawless masterpiece in flesh.\nShe embraces you, lifts your marble-cold fingers. Together you'll return home, where art reigns eternal.", "timestamp": "2025-06-27T08:17:41.855000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1388070774568386570", "filename": "3._-Death_by_Beauty-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 5575724, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1388070499476705331/1388070774568386570/3._-Death_by_Beauty-.mp3?ex=69ccd4a5&is=69cb8325&hm=23ed1321b36b14b52dbf94ab54848fe514bd49f66c5a49cf7a05b5a1302eaf85&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1388070499476705331", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：珊EP·石化藝術", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
